        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 320,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7200,
            "LocalizeKR": "미식에 있어서 중요한 것은,\n요리와 상대… 그리고 시기.",
            "LocalizeJP": "美食にとって大切なものは、\n料理と相手……そして時期。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9300,
            "LocalizeKR": "그것들 만큼이나,\n미식을 즐기는 상황도,\n빼놓을 수 없는 존재죠.",
            "LocalizeJP": "それと同じくらい、\nシチュエーションも\nなくてはならない存在です。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 340,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10000,
            "LocalizeKR": "우후훗. 그런고로, 오늘은 서로\n먹여 주기를 해 보도록 할까요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "うふふっ。ですので、\n今日は食べさせあいっこを\nいたしましょう？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13833,
            "LocalizeKR": "우선은 저부터…\n자, 선생님. 입을 벌리고…\n아~ 해 주세요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "まずは私から……\nはい、先生。\nお口を開けて……\nあ～んしてください。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 360,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7500,
            "LocalizeKR": "저, 정말, 어서요.\n저도… 부끄럽습니다만…",
            "LocalizeJP": "も、もう、早くなさって\nください。私も……\n恥ずかしいのですが……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10057,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005701,
            "DisplayOrder": 370,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11333,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님께서 먹어 주실 때까지,\n저는 이대로 있을거랍니다?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生が口にしてくださるまで、\n私はこのまま続けますわよ？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
